  standBesideKingPoint: {fileID: 1130905785}
  cutsceneLines:
  - "H\u1EE1i d\xE2n l\xE0ng!  Ng\xE0y h\u1ED9i d\xE2ng b\xE1nh \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EBFn.
    Vua H\xF9ng m\u1EDF cu\u1ED9c thi d\xE2ng b\xE1nh \u0111\u1EC3 t\u01B0\u1EDFng
    nh\u1EDB c\xF4ng lao c\u1EE7a Lang Li\xEAu.  Ai l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c b\xE1nh
    ch\u01B0ng v\xE0 b\xE1nh gi\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EE7, ngon l\xE0nh,
    s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c d\xE2ng l\u1EC5 v\u1EADt l\xEAn Vua H\xF9ng.  M\u1ECDi
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi h\xE3y b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u thu th\u1EADp nguy\xEAn li\u1EC7u
    v\xE0 chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB b\u1EBFp n\u1EA5u!"
